Join the Conversation To find out more about Facebook commenting please read the Conversation Guidelines and FAQs PODCAST: Cyclones showcase super start, sketchy finish The Des Moines Register 9:07 p.m. CDT October 20, 2015 Cyclone Insider (Photo: The Register) 
Things started so well. 
Iowa State hung with TCU for 30 minutes and put together an offensive tour de force for one quarter, but the effort unraveled come last Saturday's second half in Ames. 
Tommy Birch and KXnO's Chris Williams put a bow on the TCU game, from its stellar first quarter to, well, everything else, in the latest "Cyclone Insider" hour. 
Then they dive deep into what's realistic for the rest of the season and just when Joel Lanning will see more snaps before touching on Big 12 basketball media day in Kansas City. Read or Share this story: http://dmreg.co/1LJHrch TOP VIDEOS
